Class ResolvableTypes

java.lang.Object
io.github.lengors.scoutdesk.domain.spring.core.services.ResolvableTypes
public final class ResolvableTypes extends Object
Utility class for working with Spring's ResolvableType. Provides methods to compare and flatten type hierarchies.
